            <span class="text-navy font-semibold">Disc Centrifuge Parts Glossary</span>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-light mt-1">Illustrated glossary of all disc stack centrifuge bowl components.</p>
          </a>
          <a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge-lubrication/" class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-4 shadow-sm hover:border-gold transition-colors">
